-Wen!
-Wen Chengye!

635
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:33,030
Wen Chengye,

636
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:35,030
don't forget the team meeting
this afternoon.

637
00:28:35,030 --> 00:28:37,490
-Got it.
-It's about us reaching the finals!

638
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:39,070
Did you hear that?

639
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:40,310
We made it to the finals!

640
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:41,310
Got it!

641
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:42,680
Qin Ao is so handsome.

642
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:44,140
They made it to the finals.

643
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:45,680
Qin Ao is so cool!

644
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:47,750
Qin Ao, you're so cool!

645
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:49,310
Let's go watch it together!

646
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:51,950
So cool!

647
