673
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:05,070
I'm really happy today.

674
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:08,340
Seeing how far you've all come

675
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:10,640
makes every bit of it worthwhile—

676
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,200
all those hours I spent

677
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:15,600
wearing my reading glasses,
helping you fill your composition grids

678
00:30:15,600 --> 00:30:18,930
one square at a time,
and copying English poems line by line.

679
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,060
It was all worth it.

680
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,000
Alright.

681
00:30:24,510 --> 00:30:26,140
I'm here today

682
00:30:26,170 --> 00:30:27,570
representing the school

683
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,160
to talk to you all about

684
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:31,720
the special admission policy.

685
00:30:37,240 --> 00:30:38,840
I think they had it last year.

686
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:41,750
Special admission.

687
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,200
What exactly is it?

688
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:45,960
Well, the football game

689
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:47,680
is about to start,

690
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,000
and it's the finals.

691
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,510
If you win

692
00:30:51,510 --> 00:30:53,240
the championship,

693
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:56,200
3 players among you

694
00:30:56,200 --> 00:31:00,480
