for special university admission.

695
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:03,850
That's what special admission means.

696
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,750
Director,

697
00:31:06,770 --> 00:31:09,350
how many points can it lower
the admission threshold by?

698
00:31:09,350 --> 00:31:10,280
I looked into it.

699
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:12,330
Based on your current grades,

700
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:14,440
if you guys push a little harder,

701
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:16,220
you should be able to reach

702
00:31:16,010 --> 00:31:17,760
[Special Admission]

703
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:19,320
the score requirement
for special admission.

704
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:22,160
Does it only apply
if we win the championship?

705
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:23,960
Well, of course, the runner-up works too.

706
00:31:23,960 --> 00:31:25,160
It's just that there won't be

707
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,000
those 3

708
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,640
fixed special admission slots.

709
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:30,500
So obviously,
winning the championship is better.

710
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,440
Really,

711
00:31:32,470 --> 00:31:35,680
the school hopes you can
achieve good results.

712
00:31:36,150 --> 00:31:39,250
[Special Admission]

713
00:31:36,380 --> 00:31:37,650
But...

714
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,200
I'd

715
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:42,030
also like to say

716
00:31:42,370 --> 00:31:44,210
a few words from the heart.

717
00:31:48,940 --> 00:31:50,670
I still remember two years ago,

718
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:53,680
when you first came to this school.

719
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:56,070
You were even rowdier back then.

720
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:57,480
But

721
00:31:57,790 --> 00:32:00,480
your eyes were shining with light.

722
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:02,440
I thought to myself then

723
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:05,720
that you were a bunch of good boys
with ambition.

724
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:09,680
But not long after,

725
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:11,200
your class fell apart,

726
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:13,200
and so did your spirits.

727
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,270
Especially

728
00:32:14,550 --> 00:32:16,920
that light in your eyes—

729
00:32:17,610 --> 00:32:19,550
I could no longer see it.

730
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,720
It worried me deeply.

731
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:24,710
I really wanted to do something for you,

732
00:32:25,120 --> 00:32:26,030
but

733
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:29,310
there was only so much I could do.

734
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:31,160
Later,

735
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:32,920
Mr. Lin found me

736
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:35,160
and asked me to be this "mystery person"

737
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:37,680
to carry out this secret plan.

738
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,240
I was very happy.

739
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,980
I agreed on the spot

740
00:32:40,980 --> 00:32:42,780
without a moment's hesitation.

741
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,200
I have always believed

742
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:49,200
that as an educator,

743
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:52,000
we must never let

744
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:54,720
the fire in the students' hearts go out.

745
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:01,870
And now, I'm truly happy

746
00:33:02,070 --> 00:33:02,680
to see

747
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:05,540
that fire burning bright
in your hearts once again.

748
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:07,550
Really.

749
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:10,270
No matter whether you win

750
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:12,200
the championship this time or not,

751
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,200
in my heart,

752
00:33:15,750 --> 00:33:16,960
you are all the best.

753
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,440
I can proudly say

754
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:22,070
that I

755
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:27,070
am a teacher of Hongjing No. 8 High School's
star football team.

756
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:29,400
Our football players

757
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:32,310
are the best.

758
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,460
The absolute best.

759
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:46,200
Qian,

760
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:50,000
the other day, Chen Jianghe and I
snuck off with your bike

761
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,400
and ended up breaking it.

762
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:54,350
Now it makes a rattling noise
whenever you ride it.

763
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:55,970
Don't worry.

764
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:58,370
I'll definitely fix it for you.

765
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:00,030
Good.

766
00:34:00,750 --> 00:34:01,960
Since you're being real with me,

767
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,690
I've got to be real with you too.

768
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:06,270
I wasn't going to tell you at first,

769
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:07,070
but now

770
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:09,670
I'll share another
piece of good news with you.

771
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:11,150
In order to

772
00:34:11,150 --> 00:34:15,150
let you focus wholeheartedly on
preparing for the finals,

773
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:16,730
starting next week,

774
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:19,790
the school is giving you 2 weeks off

775
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:22,230
for intensive training!

776
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:24,280
Two weeks?

777
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:27,840
Thank you, Director!

778
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,670
Thank you, Director!

779
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:32,710
Alright, alright!

780
00:34:32,710 --> 00:34:34,480
M-M-My job here is done.

781
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:35,190
You guys, enjoy the milk tea.

782
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:36,150
-Enjoy the milk tea.
-Okay, okay.

783
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:37,710
Bye-bye! Bye-bye!

784
00:34:38,710 --> 00:34:39,920
See you tomorrow!

785
00:34:40,630 --> 00:34:41,920
That's great!

786
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:43,880
Fight on, guys!

787
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,320
-Fight on!
-Yeah!

788
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,400
Just got the news—

789
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:53,280
Hengjiu defeated
their opponent 7-0 with ease

790
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,710
and advanced to
the Youth Super League finals.

791
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:56,710
We fought tooth and nail to advance,

792
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:58,400
while they cruised through.

793
00:34:58,630 --> 00:35:00,630
That final boss really is a final boss,

794
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:02,360
scoring like that in the semifinals.

795
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,510
They're just

796
00:35:03,510 --> 00:35:04,840
in a league of their own.

797
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:06,570
When we face them in the finals,

798
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,440
it'll be like two bitter rivals

799
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,640
going head-to-head.

800
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,290
Starting tomorrow,

801
00:35:13,660 --> 00:35:16,230
[Little Savage Tribe]

802
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,710
we'll focus on analyzing
Hengjiu's playing style and discuss

803
00:35:15,710 --> 00:35:18,670
-targeted tactics for the finals.
-Coach has new strategies.

804
00:35:18,670 --> 00:35:19,760
But

805
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,480
no matter how good the tactics are,

806
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:23,340
can we really beat the final boss?

807
00:35:23,550 --> 00:35:25,710
After all, in our last match against them,

808
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:27,510
they scored 11 goals against us.

809
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:38,440
You can still eat?

810
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:40,230
Why wouldn't I?

811
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:42,400
Is being this dejected

812
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:44,130
going to help you win the match?

813
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:49,030
Well said.

814
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:50,840
Eat as much as we can now,

815
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:53,320
and give it everything
we've got on the field later.

816
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:54,030
Not eating?

817
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,210
I'm eating then.

818
00:35:57,030 --> 00:35:58,230
Come on, eat up.

819
00:35:59,510 --> 00:36:01,840
I think we should stop being intimidated.

820
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:03,280
Who cares if they're the final boss?

821
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:05,630
At least we have a chance
to compete against them.

822
00:36:05,630 --> 00:36:06,880
Cheer up, guys.

823
00:36:07,230 --> 00:36:08,160
Just do our best.

824
00:36:08,230 --> 00:36:09,070
-Come on, guys.
-Yeah.

825
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,190
Cheer up, guys.

826
00:36:11,230 --> 00:36:12,000
That's right.

827
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,930
And we've got a world-class coach.

828
00:36:18,150 --> 00:36:19,940
We have to master the 4-4-2 Formation.

829
00:36:19,940 --> 00:36:22,000
That way, we won't panic
and let Yongchuan Hengjiu

830
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:23,510
throw us off our game.

831
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,250
So where are we going to train?

832
00:36:26,250 --> 00:36:27,280
Where else?

833
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,550
The school field.

834
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:31,510
We only have two weeks left.

835
00:36:31,510 --> 00:36:33,280
And they have PE classes there every day.

836
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:34,590
Realistically, we only have

837
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:35,990
about half a day to train.

838
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:37,440
Besides, the school closes every day,

839
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:39,190
so we won't even be able to use the field.

840
00:36:39,190 --> 00:36:40,790
And now with new tactics too,

841
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:43,610
there's simply no time
to get everything in sync.

842
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:45,760
That makes sense.

843
00:36:46,250 --> 00:36:48,230
Then, where does Yongchuan Hengjiu

844
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:49,440
usually train?

845
00:36:51,370 --> 00:36:53,030
This is their training field.

846
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,740
-Oh my god.
-What the hell?

847
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:57,550
I've never trained at a place

848
00:36:57,550 --> 00:36:58,810
this high-end before.

849
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:01,230
So what if their field's so fancy?

850
00:37:01,230 --> 00:37:02,840
Doesn't mean a thing if you can't win,

851
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,590
right?

852
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:04,440
Don't chicken out.

853
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,400
Just go for it.

854
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:06,070
Yeah.

855
00:37:06,070 --> 00:37:08,360
When have I ever been afraid of anyone?

856
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:10,150
-You can't defeat me.
-Let me take another look.

857
00:37:10,150 --> 00:37:11,000
Let me see.

858
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:12,940
Get your spirits up, will you?

859
00:37:13,070 --> 00:37:13,630
Wait.

860
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,210
Are you serious?

861
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:16,630
As for aerobic endurance,

862
00:37:16,630 --> 00:37:18,710
I think our midfielders are the ones
who need to focus on it.

863
00:37:18,710 --> 00:37:20,000
Zheng Ren, what do you think?

864
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,190
Actually, I think aerobic endurance

865
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:22,590
helps with

866
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:23,230
those short bursts

867
00:37:23,230 --> 00:37:24,880
of explosive movement, you know?

868
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,440
And Fu, I think
you should train more on that too.

869
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:27,070
Yeah, we need to work on it together.

870
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:27,880
No.

871
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:28,940
My former manager,

872
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,320
do me a favor.

873
00:37:31,550 --> 00:37:32,190
Zheng Ren!

874
00:37:32,190 --> 00:37:32,590
Pass the ball!

875
00:37:32,590 --> 00:37:34,190
Over here!

876
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:38,590
Chen Jianghe!

877
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,790
It's okay, it's okay.

878
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:42,130
Keep moving forward, forward.

879
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:42,980
Zheng Ren!

880
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:45,760
You've watched this match footage
over a dozen times already.

881
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,480
Yeah.

882
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:49,330
The more I watch it,
the more anxious I get.

883
00:37:49,870 --> 00:37:51,310
What should we do?

884
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:52,630
We don't even have
a proper training facility

885
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:53,800
for specialized drills.

886
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,190
Are we definitely going to lose?

887
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:56,320
Don't worry.

888
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:59,110
I'm their coach.

889
00:37:59,110 --> 00:38:00,320
This is my job.

890
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:01,800
I'm confiscating

891
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:03,130
your source of anxiety.

892
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:08,510
All set.

893
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:12,280
Come on.

894
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:14,770
Let's go out for a drink.

895
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,590
A drink?

896
00:38:17,190 --> 00:38:20,230
If you want to drink, why don't we
just make something at your place?

897
00:38:20,230 --> 00:38:21,890
The atmosphere is different.

898
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:22,920
Going out for a walk

899
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,720
will help you feel less anxious.

900
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:27,550
I don't want to move.

901
00:38:27,550 --> 00:38:29,110
I'm not in the mood.

902
00:38:29,710 --> 00:38:31,460
If you come with me,

903
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:32,810
I'll give you a big gift

904
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:34,540
that you'll definitely love.

905
00:38:36,230 --> 00:38:38,430
Bigger than that PhD application form?

906
00:38:38,550 --> 00:38:40,210
It holds a different meaning.

907
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:42,110
Fine.

908
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:05,510
The stars by the sea are so bright.

909
00:39:08,230 --> 00:39:09,480
If you like,

910
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,670
we can come here often.

911
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:12,400
We can also see stars like these

912
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:15,610
from the rooftop
where we have tutoring classes.

913
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:18,320
I think a certain someone

914
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,590
is just lazy.

915
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:28,190
After building up the suspense
for so long,

916
00:39:28,190 --> 00:39:29,400
you can

917
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,800
bring out the gift for me.

918
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:33,920
"All set."

919
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,760
I heard your call

920
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:36,880
with Yu Bo.

921
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:38,590
When he said "all set,"

922
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:41,190
did you mean
you've secured a training ground?

923
00:39:43,940 --> 00:39:44,980
I'm wrong?

924
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:48,550
Then you can call Chairman Wang Genfa

925
00:39:48,550 --> 00:39:49,480
now.

926
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:53,320
Chairman Wang Genfa is very stingy.

927
00:39:53,770 --> 00:39:55,100
Then I'll make the call.

928
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:00,510
You guessed right.

929
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:02,840
I've booked the best training facility
in Hongjing

930
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,640
and a hotel
where the team can stay together.

931
00:40:04,640 --> 00:40:06,570
And I didn't book Hengjiu's place.

932
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,090
I paid for it myself.

933
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:13,480
No more words.

934
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,630
Let's drink to it.

935
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,150
Cheers.

936
00:40:25,050 --> 00:40:25,860
Are you cold?

937
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,000
A bit.

938
00:40:29,490 --> 00:40:30,410
Come on.

939
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:50,680
A crab!

940
00:40:57,200 --> 00:40:58,680
Where did it go?

941
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,150
Where did you get it?

942
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:19,400
They say when fireworks burn,

943
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:21,200
they create a "wish frequency."

944
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:24,320
If your heartbeat syncs with it
at that moment,

945
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:26,380
your wish will definitely come true.

946
00:41:28,590 --> 00:41:30,440
Looks like you've been reading

947
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:32,770
quite a few psychology books, Coach Wang.

948
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,280
Give it a try?

949
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,460
Let's make a wish together

950
00:41:39,670 --> 00:41:41,070
to win the championship.

951
00:41:48,630 --> 00:41:49,800
You know what?

952
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:53,930
These sparks are made of magnesium.

953
00:41:54,190 --> 00:41:57,880
Magnesium reacts with carbon dioxide.

954
00:41:57,880 --> 00:42:00,680
So you can't put them out
with a fire extinguisher.

955
00:42:02,320 --> 00:42:05,180
You've switched to
being a chemistry teacher, huh?

956
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:14,710
Wait.

957
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,150
To put out the fire...

958
00:42:26,070 --> 00:42:28,510
you just need to cover a large area

959
00:42:26,890 --> 00:42:28,790
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

960
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:31,150
to cut off the carbon dioxide.

961
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:31,890
♪ On the summer night ♪

962
00:42:32,290 --> 00:42:37,760
♪ Like stars that glow so bright ♪

963
00:42:39,310 --> 00:42:41,720
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

964
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:48,340
♪ Lost in a dream secretly ♪

965
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:56,920
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

966
00:42:57,530 --> 00:43:03,210
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

967
00:43:03,750 --> 00:43:04,680
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

968
00:43:14,190 --> 00:43:15,280
-The kids are urging us...
-Let's go.

969
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:16,340
Let's go find them.

970
00:43:22,110 --> 00:43:23,670
Good evening.

971
00:43:24,360 --> 00:43:25,440
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

972
00:43:25,550 --> 00:43:26,590
Ms. Lin, Coach!

973
00:43:26,590 --> 00:43:27,000
Play football...

974
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:28,880
-What's wrong?
-I can walk by myself.

975
00:43:28,880 --> 00:43:30,540
-Okay, okay.
-Let me show you.

976
00:43:31,510 --> 00:43:32,770
Ms. Lin is here. Ms. Lin is here.

977
00:43:32,770 --> 00:43:33,760
-Ms. Lin.
-Coach.

978
00:43:33,760 --> 00:43:36,290
-You called us here this late...
-Attention.

979
00:43:37,590 --> 00:43:39,070
Big drinker, tiny tolerance.

980
00:43:39,070 --> 00:43:39,880
She's drunk.

981
00:43:42,880 --> 00:43:44,480
Please sit down, everyone.

982
00:43:46,280 --> 00:43:47,810
Listen to your supervisor.

983
00:43:53,390 --> 00:43:54,850
Sit... Where should I sit?

984
00:44:09,840 --> 00:44:11,280
Do you still remember

985
00:44:11,750 --> 00:44:15,230
how you felt
when you signed this football?

986
00:44:16,480 --> 00:44:17,960
Signed football.

987
00:44:17,960 --> 00:44:19,280
When we make it big,

988
00:44:19,280 --> 00:44:21,000
this'll be priceless.

989
00:44:28,480 --> 00:44:31,740
Now it really feels like a football team
with star players.

990
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:32,400
Yes.

991
00:44:32,400 --> 00:44:33,280
Technique.

992
00:44:34,030 --> 00:44:34,960
My turn, my turn.

993
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:38,030
Don't be so quick to forget.

994
00:44:39,150 --> 00:44:40,720
It's for Fu's sake.

995
00:44:40,760 --> 00:44:42,670
I'll just scribble something.

996
00:44:44,400 --> 00:44:45,470
Cool.

997
00:44:47,770 --> 00:44:49,350
Quit pretending, dude.

998
00:44:50,480 --> 00:44:51,110
Here, pen.

999
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:52,840
So annoying.

1000
00:45:02,590 --> 00:45:03,280
Alright, boys.

1001
00:45:03,280 --> 00:45:04,030
It's about time.

1002
00:45:04,030 --> 00:45:05,560
Hurry up and go to training.

1003
00:45:06,180 --> 00:45:08,150
[Feng Suo]

1004
00:45:15,280 --> 00:45:17,140
Whoever wasn't serious back then

1005
00:45:17,550 --> 00:45:19,320
knows it in their own heart.

1006
00:45:38,920 --> 00:45:40,150
Actually,

1007
00:45:40,630 --> 00:45:42,630
there's something very important

1008
00:45:42,630 --> 00:45:44,070
I still haven't done.

1009
00:45:54,920 --> 00:45:59,270
[Feng Suo]

1010
00:45:59,670 --> 00:46:01,120
[Lin]

1011
00:46:05,410 --> 00:46:06,350
[Lin Wanxing]

1012
00:46:12,340 --> 00:46:15,300
Are you willing to sign it now, Mr. Coach?

1013
00:46:14,330 --> 00:46:15,640
♪ A starlit night ♪

1014
00:46:16,220 --> 00:46:20,740
♪ Secrets falling into my palm ♪

1015
00:46:21,510 --> 00:46:22,890
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

1016
00:46:23,550 --> 00:46:27,580
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

1017
00:46:28,170 --> 00:46:29,580
[Lin Wanxing]

1018
00:46:28,610 --> 00:46:29,960
♪ Lasting memories ♪

1019
00:46:30,720 --> 00:46:35,040
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

1020
00:46:35,820 --> 00:46:36,810
♪ To run toward you ♪

1021
00:46:37,370 --> 00:46:41,870
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

1022
00:46:44,420 --> 00:46:45,750
[Wang Fa]

1023
00:46:45,420 --> 00:46:46,700
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

1024
00:46:47,890 --> 00:46:49,220
♪ Because you're with me ♪

1025
00:46:52,370 --> 00:46:53,620
♪ The light shimmers ♪

1026
00:46:55,070 --> 00:46:56,360
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

1027
00:46:57,980 --> 00:46:59,040
♪ Running towards you ♪

1028
00:46:59,890 --> 00:47:01,000
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

1029
00:47:05,040 --> 00:47:05,950
♪ Walk side by side ♪

1030
00:47:06,850 --> 00:47:08,490
♪ Become ourselves ♪

1031
00:47:10,890 --> 00:47:11,920
♪ Amid the storm ♪

1032
00:47:12,660 --> 00:47:16,940
♪ As our breaths slowly intertwine ♪

1033
00:47:17,650 --> 00:47:18,770
♪ Heartbeats alternating ♪

